title: Vernon Kay takeover Pete Tong Friday show 10/04/2009
description:
Vernon Kay takeover Pete Tong's Friday show 
Friday 10th April 2009

To officially start the Easter weekend... Mr Vernon Kay!

Pete is off so Vernon steps up...with some hot new tracks and a vintage Soulwax Hot Mix...

Broadcast: BBC Radio 1, International 

Tracklist:

Jonny L- 'Dreaming' (Nero UK)
Pixie Lott- 'Mama Do' (Linus Remix) (Mercury)

Dub Guru- 'U Got 2 Know' (Maelstrom)

Carl Cox On The Phone
